fety%20threat%20or%20hazard%20to%20passengers.%20However%2C%20the%20exact%20cause%20will%20be%20further%20investigated%20in%20this%20case%2C''%20DMRC%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20video%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20In%20reference%20to%20a%20viral%20video%20in%20which%20a%20minor%20fire%20is%20seen%20emanating%20from%20the%20roof%20of%20a%20train%2C%20this%20is%20to%20clarify%20that%20the%20incident%20pertains%20the%20to%20a%20train%20at%20Rajiv%20Chowk%20station%20heading%20towards%20Vaishali%20around%206%3A21%20pm%20today%3A%20DMRC%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20extant%20incident%20was%20the%20case%20of%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fi8To6qXgha%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fi8To6qXgha%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1795142161291411534%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affected%20pantograph%20was%20immediately%20put%20out%20of%20service%20and%20the%20train%20continued%20its%20onward%20journey%20as%20usual%20after%20around%205%20minutes%20of%20troubleshooting%20with%20the%20remaining%20pantographs%20of%20the%20train%2C%20DMRC%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20pantograph%20is%20an%20apparatus%20mounted%20on%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20train%20and%C2%A0collects%20the%20electricity%20needed%20to%20power%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Metro%20has%20been%20a%20lifeline%20for%20Delhiites%2C%20ever%20since%20it%20became%20operational%20back%20in%202002.%C2%A0Presently%2C%20the%C2%A0Delhi%20Metro%C2%A0network%20consists%20of%20about%20392.44%20km%20with%20288%20stations%C2%A0across%2