E%2C%20the%20investor%20Larry%20Connor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20show%20people%20worldwide%20that%20while%20the%20ocean%20is%20extremely%20powerful%2C%20it%20can%20be%20wonderful%20and%20enjoyable%20and%20really%20kind%20of%20life-changing%20if%20you%20go%20about%20it%20the%20right%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Connor%20has%20designed%20a%20Triton%204000%2F2%20Abyssal%20Explorer%2C%20a%20%2420%20million%20vessel%2C%20which%20will%20carry%20out%20the%20voyage.%20It%20has%20been%20named%20%26quot%3B4000%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20depth%20in%20meters%20it%20can%20reach.%20%26quot%3BPatrick%20has%20been%20thinking%20about%20and%20designing%20this%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20But%20we%20didn't%20have%20the%20materials%20and%20technology.%20You%20couldn't%20have%20built%20this%20sub%20five%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETriton%20Submarines%20co-founder%20Patrick%20Lahey%20told%20%3Cem%3EWSJ%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Mr%20Connor%20called%20him%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20Titan%20sub%20implosion%20and%20said%20that%20need%20to%20build%20a%20sub%20that%20could%20dive%20safely.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20what%20we%20need%20to%20do%20is%20build%20a%20sub%20that%20can%20dive%20to%20(Titanic-level%20depths)%20repeatedly%20and%20safely%20and%20demonstrate%20to%20the%20world%20that%20you%20guys%20can%20do%20that%2C%20and%20that%20Titan%20was%20a%20contraption%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lahey%20told%20about%20the%20billionaire.%20However%2C%20the%20real%20estate%20investor%20has%20not%20mentioned%20any%20specific%20date%20or%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lahey%20was%20among%20the%20numerous%20industry%20critics%20who%20attacked%20OceanGate%20before%20and%20following%20the%20catastrophe%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20questionable%20safety%20standards.%20Following%20the%20implosion%2C%20he%20called%20OceanGate%20CEO%20Stockton%20Rush's%20strategy%20for%20getting%20people%20on%20board%20%26quot%3Bquite%20predatory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%