tions%2C%20providing%20a%20holistic%20view%20of%20his%20health.%20Within%20six%20months%2C%20the%20results%20were%20remarkable.%20Devlin%20lost%20over%2040%20pounds%20(18%20kg)%2C%20achieved%20diabetes%20remission%2C%20lowered%20his%20blood%20pressure%20and%20cholesterol%2C%20and%20even%20reduced%20his%20medication%20reliance%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Fscience%2Fhealth%2Fnews%2Ffacing-an-early-death-a-ceo-created-a-digital-twin-of-his-body-it-transformed-his-health-%2Farticleshow%2F110421330.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFueling%20his%20transformation%20was%20a%20dietary%20shift.%20Devlin%20prioritised%20vegetables%20like%20broccoli%20and%20cauliflower%2C%20swapped%20processed%20snacks%20for%20nuts%2C%20and%20even%20created%20diabetic-friendly%20pancakes%20using%20almond%20flour.%20%26quot%3BDiabetes%20advice%20can%20be%20confusing%2C%26quot%3B%20Devlin%20shared.%20%26quot%3BThey%20focus%20on%20restrictions%2C%20not%20embracing%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonaldson%20said%20the%20personalised%20insights%20transformed%20his%20understanding%20of%20his%20body%20and%20the%20challenges%20he%20faced.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20his%20diabetes%20is%20in%20remission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevlin's%20secret%20weapon%3F%20Protein-packed%20pancakes%20made%20with%20almond%20flour%20offer%20more%20protein%2C%20fibre%2C%20and%20a%20lower%20blood%20sugar%20impact%20compared%20to%20regular%20flour.%20He%20also%20incorporated%20more%20movement%2C%20aiming%20for%2010%2C000%20daily%20steps.%20%26quot%3BStarting%20any%20new%20exercise%20routine%20is%20tough%2C%26quot%3B%20Devlin%20admitted.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20gets%20easier!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fhealth-topics%2Fdiabetes%23tab%3Dtab_1%5C%22%3EWorld%20Health%20Organisation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%20422%20million%20people%20world