20a%20time%2C%20that%20I%20should%20make%20the%20countrymen%20aware%20of%20the%20biggest%20crisis%20that%20is%20coming.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20have%20been%20explaining%20this%20to%20the%20people.%20The%20basic%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20is%20being%20violated%20and%20that%20too%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20vote%20bank%20politics...%20Those%20who%20call%20themselves%20well-wishers%20of%20the%20Dalits%2C%20Tribals%2C%20are%20in%20reality%20their%20staunch%20enemies...There%20is%20an%20imprint%20of%20the%20Muslim%20League%20in%20their%20manifesto...Do%20you%20want%20to%20destroy%20the%20coming%20generations%20also%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20vote-bank%3F...%20I%20will%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20my%20Dalit%2C%20Tribal%2C%20OBC%20brothers%20and%20sisters.%20And%20that's%20why%20I'm%20fighting%20the%20battle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20those%20who%20call%20themselves%20the%20biggest%20sympathisers%20of%20the%20backward%20communities%20are%20in%20reality%20their%20biggest%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20opposition%20of%20converting%20educational%20institutions%20into%20minority%20institutions%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20highlighted%20that%20this%20action%20ended%20protections%20for%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20and%20OBC%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20swiftly%20converted%20educational%20institutions%20into%20minority%20institutions%2C%20thereby%20eliminating%20reservations.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Jamia%20Millia%20University%20was%20designated%20a%20minority%20institution%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20reservations%2C%20affecting%20both%20admissions%20and%20jobs.%20It%20later%20emerged%20that%20around%2010%2C000%20such%20institutions%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20reach%20of%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20and%20OBC%20protections%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20made%20arrangements%20for%20it%20and%20even%20leveraged%20it%20for%20vote%20bank%20politics.%20When%20this%20concerning%20issue%20came%20to%20my%20attention%2C%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20my%20duty%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20expressed%20his%20concerns%20about%20the%20Congress%20party's%20stance%20on%20reservations%2C%20which%20became%20evident%20to%20him%20after%20they%20released%20their%20manifesto.%20He%20recounted%20his%20reaction%20to%20the%20manifesto%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20Muslim%20League's%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20in%20its%20manifesto%2C%20'Nyay%20Patra'%20released%20on%20April%205%20mentioned%20that%20it%20will%20pass%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%20to%20raise%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20cap%20on%20reservations%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20manifesto%20gave%20me%20another%20shock.%20And%20that's%20why%20when%20I%20saw%20the%20first%20manifesto%2C%20my%20first%20thought%20was%20that%20this%20manifesto%20has%20the%20imprint%20of%20Muslim%20League.%20So%20for%20two-three%20days%20they%20thought%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20respond%20to%20this.%20When%20they%20did%20not%20give%20any%20answer%2C%20that%20is%20when%20I%20started%20opening%20up%20one%20by%20one.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20this%20country%2C%20they%20say%20that%20we%20will%20also%20fix%20quota%20for%20minorities%20in%20sports.%20Today%2C%20children%20from%20Punjab%20are%20doing%20very%20well%20in%20the%20world%20of%20sports.%20Our%20youth%20in%20Bengal%20are%20doing%20very%20well%20in%20football.%20Our%20youth%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20doing%20very%20well%20in%20athletics.%20The%20youth%20put%20in%20so%20much%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20they%20wake%20up%20at%204%20in%20the%20morning.%20Congress%20says%20this%20will%20now%20go%20to%20the%20minority%2C%20so%20where%20will%20my%20hardworking%20young%20man%20go%3F%20What%20will%20happen%20to%20him%3F%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20criticized%20the%20Congress%20party's%20proposal%20to%20reserve%20government%20tenders%20for%20minorities.%20He%20explained%20that%20for%20critical%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20constructing%20an%20important%20bridge%2C%20the%20contract%20should%20go%20to%20the%20company%20with%20the%20best%20track%20record%2C%20resources%2C%20capabilities%2C%20and%20qualifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuppose%20today%20a%20very%20important%20bridge%20is%20being%20built...%20who%20will%20build%20the%20bridge%3F%20The%20one%20who%20has%20a%20track%20record%2C%20the%20one%20who%20has%20the%20resources%2C%20the%20one%20who%20has%20the%20capability%2C%20the%20one%20who%20can%20perform%2C%20the%20one%20who%20meets%20all%20the%20requirements.%20There%20is%20competition%20in%20that.%20And%20the%20one%20who%20wins%20the%20competition%20gets%20the%20tender.%20They%20don't%20say%20this.%20All%20this%20happens%20later.%20Now%20tell%20me%2C%20if%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20only%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%2C%20quotas%20are%20given%2C%20that%20bridge%20will%20be%20built%20and%20people%20will%20be%20killed%2C%20then%20who%20will%20be%20responsible%3F%20Do%20you%20want%20to%20destroy%20the%20future%20generations%20for%20the%20vote%20bank%3F%20So%20these%20were%20some%20topics%20which%20the%20Congress%20brought%20in%20their%20politics%20of%20vote%20bank%20and%20it%20is%20now%20upto%20me%20to%20save%20the%20rights%20of%20my%20OBC%2C%20SC%2C%20ST%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20the%20opposition%20related%20to%20reservation%20came%20to%20light%20after%20the%20recent%20decision%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20to%20cancel%20OBC%20certificates%20was%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20modus%20operandi.%20First%2C%20they%20started%20the%20sin%20of%20giving%20it%20to%20minorities%20by%20making%20a%20law%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20lost%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20High%20Court%20rejected%20it%20because%20the%20Constitution%20does%20not%20allow%20it.%20So%20they%20cleverly%20started%20the%20game%20from%20the%20back%20door%20and%20these%20people%20overnight%20made%20all%20the%20castes%20of%20Muslim%20as%20OBCs%20and%20they%20robbed%20the%20OBCs%20of%20their%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20High%20Court's%20judgment%20came%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20such%20a%20big%20fraud%20was%20taking%20place.%20But%20what%20is%20even%20more%20unfortunate%20is%20that%20for%20vote%20bank%20politics%2C%20now%20they%20are%20also%20abusing%20the%20judiciary.%20And%20they%20are%20even%20saying%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20happens%2C%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20court.%20This%20situation%20cannot%20be%20acceptable%20under%20any%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20phases%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20over%20and%20the%20final%20phase%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%201%20where%2057%20constituencies%20in%208%20states.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20elections%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20June%204.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716871620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fp3t75pu_pm-modi-ani-_625x300_28_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-minorities-biggest-enemy-pm-says-reservation-key-issue-of-2024-5761417%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Accusing%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20indulging%20in%20%26quot%3Bvote%20bank%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20criticised%20opposition%20parties%20for%20undermining%20the%20constitutional%20rights%2