150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110483954%2Cimgsize-54842.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fchhaya-kadam-opens-up-on-being-teased-for-dancing-at-the-cannes-red-carpet-retorts-why-not%2Farticleshow%2F110483977.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110483977.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EReflecting%20on%20whose%20idea%20the%20dance%20was%2C%20Chhaya%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20say%20for%20sure%2C%20but%20it%20might%20have%20been%20me.%20Someone%20from%20Mumbai%20joked%2C%20'You%20were%20dancing%20as%20if%20you%20were%20in%20your%20own%20courtyard.'%20To%20which%20I%20responded%2C%20'Why%20not%3F'%20Being%20part%20of%20the%20main%20competition%20after%2030%20years%2C%20and%20winning%20an%20award%2C%20is%20a%20significant%20accomplishment.%20Why%20conform%20to%20norms%3F%20We%20express%20our%20joy%20by%20dancing%20freely.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fchhaya-kadam-opens-up-on-being-teased-for-dancing-at-the-cannes-red-carpet-retorts-why-not%2Farticleshow%2F110483977.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chennai%20Start-Up's%20Rocket%20Launch%2C%20Game-Changer%20For%20Space%20Tech%2C%20Called%20Off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20Cosmos%2C%20a%20pioneering%20private%20space%20start-up%20in%20India%2C%20faced%20yet%20another%20hurdle%20today%20as%20the%20test%20launch%20of%20their%20rocket%2C%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20(Suborbital%20Tech%20Demonstrator)%2C%20was%20called%20off%20just%20seconds%20before%20lift-off.%20This%20marks%20the%20fourth%20postponement%20for%20the%20AgniKul%20Maiden%20rocket%20launch%2C%20which%20has%20been%20beset%20by%20a%20series%20of%20technical%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20setbacks%2C%20the%20Agnikul%20team%20remains%20undeterred%2C%20demonstrating%20remarkable%20resilience%20and%20commitment%20to%20their%20mission.%20Their%20rocket%20is%20powered%20by%20an%20advanced%20engine%2C%20which%20even%20the%20seasoned%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20continues%20to%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%2C%20comprising%20many%20engineers%20in%20their%2020s%2C%20has%20shown%20exceptional%20patience%20and%20determination%20in%20the%20face%20of%20four%20such%20postponements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20delays%20are%20not%20uncommon%20in%20the%20field%20of%20space%20exploration.%20Historical%20precedents%2C%20such%20as%20the%20numerous%20delays%20faced%20by%20Boeing's%20Starliner%20launch%20with%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20illustrate%20that%20even%20the%20most%20experienced%20teams%20encounter%20obstacles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul's%20cautious%20strategy%20aligns%20with%20industry%20best%20practices%2C%20emphasising%20the%20principle%20of%20%26quot%3Bsafety%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20attempt%20was%20made%20on%20March%2022%20this%20year%20and%20was%20abandoned%20during%20countdown.%20The%20last%20attempt%20was%20made%20on%20April%207%20and%20was%20called%20off%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20before%20lift-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncubated%20at%20IIT-Madras%2C%20this%20was%20the%20first%20test%20flight%20for%20the%20start-up%2C%20founded%20in%202017%20by%20two%20young%20aerospace%20engineers%20with%20a%20dream%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Ba%20place%20where%20people%20learn%20to%20use%20fire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rocket%2C%20which%20weighs%20575%20kg%20and%20is%206.2-metre%20long%2C%20was%20supposed%20to%20lift%20off%20from%20Sriharikota%20before%20plunging%20down%20into%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20is%20powered%20by%20a%20semi-cryogenic%20engine%20that%20uses%20commercially%20available%20aviation%20turbine%20fuel%2C%20essentially%20kerosene%20and%20medical-grade%20liquid%20oxygen%2C%20says%20Moin%20SPM%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Agnikul%20Cosmos%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20has%20never%20flown%20a%20semi-cryogenic%20engine.%20It%20is%20developing%20a%202000%20kN%20thrust%20semi-cryogenic%20engine%20and%20the%20first%20ignition%20trial%20was%20conducted%20successfully%20on%20May%202.%20So%2C%20the%20Chennai-based%20start-up%20has%20achieved%20what%20no%20other%20Indian%20private%20firm%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrinath%20Ravichandran%2C%20a%20co-founder%20of%20the%20space%20start-up%2C%20had%20said%20ahead%20of%20the%20launch%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20launch%20is%20significant%20since%20it%20is%20India's%20first%20launch%20from%20a%20private%20launchpad%20and%20the%20rocket%20has%20the%20world's%20first%20single%20piece%203D%20printed%20engine%20designed%20and%20built%20indigenously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20tested%20its%20first-ever%203D-printed%20engine%20in%20ground%20tests%20on%20May%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20planned%20launch%2C%20the%20start-up%20had%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BAgnibaan%20SOrTeD%20(Suborbital%20Tech%20Demonstrator)%20is%20a%20single-stage%20launch%20vehicle%20driven%20by%20Agnikul's%20patented%20Agnilet%20engine%20-%20an%20entirely%203D-printed%2C%20single-piece%2C%206%20kN%20semi-cryogenic%20engine.%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20will%20lift%20off%20vertically%20and%20follow%20a%20predetermined%20trajectory.%20The%20trajectory%2C%20manoeuvres%20and%20various%20flight%20events%20that%20will%20occur%20during%20the%20mission%20have%20been%20configured%20to%20validate%20tech%20integral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20our%20upcoming%20orbital%20flights.%20We%20are%20excited%20to%20be%20attempting%20this%20flight%20from%20our%20own%20launch%20pad%20%5Bnamed%20Dhanush%5D%20at%20Sriharikota.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20Agnibaan's%20special%203D%20printed%20engine%20can%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20game-changer%2C%20Mr%20Moin%20told%20NDTV%20that%20it%20is%20a%20single-piece%20equipment%20and%20the%20quality%20testing%20time%20for%20such%20engines%20is%20highly%20reduced%20by%20using%203D%20printing%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engine%20is%20powered%20by%20commercially%20available%20aviation%20turbine%20fuel%20and%20liquid%20oxygen.%20This%20makes%20for%20a%20cheap%20and%20easily%20available%20non-corrosive%20fuel%20which%20can%20be%20sourced%20easily%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20also%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20launch%20rockets%20from%20multiple%20locations%20with%20minimum%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20first%2C%20Agnikul%20has%20got%20the%20go-ahead%20to%20build%20a%20special%20launchpad%20near%20the%20sea%20on%20the%20Sriharikota%20island%20with%20its%20own%20dedicated%20control%20room.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20ISRO%20opening%20up%20its%20facilities%20for%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20for%20Indian%20space%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20controlled%20flight%20of%20a%20rocket%20by%20a%20private%20company%2C%20and%20all%20precautions%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20make%20sure%20nothing%20goes%20amiss.%20If%20things%20go%20awry%2C%20then%20the%20self-destruct%20mechanism%20provided%20by%20ISRO%20can%20be%20activated%20by%20the%20Range%20Safety%20Officer%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Moin%20said%20ahead%20of%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20follows%20up%20on%20the%20first%20launch%20by%20an%20Indian%20space%20company%2C%20Skyroot%20Aerospace%20Private%20Limited%2C%20which%20in%202022%20flew%20a%20solid%20fuelled%20sounding%20rocket%20from%20Sriharikota.%20Once%20Agnibaan%20rockets%20become%20operational%2C%20Agnikul%20hopes%20to%20undertake%20launch%20on%20demand%20and%20launch%2030%20to%20300%20kg%20satellites%20into%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20to%20build%20dedicated%2C%20fully%20customisable%20and%20transportable%20launch%20vehicles%20for%20small%20satellites%20to%20Low%20Earth%20Orbits%20(LEO).%20The%20launch%20vehicle%20Agnibaan%20is%20powered%20by%20a%20single-piece%203D-printed%20engine%20that%20can%20be%20made%20in%2072%20hours%20without%20any%20human%20intervention.%20It%20is%20compatible%20with%20the%20mobile%20launch%20pad%20called%20'Dhanush'%20which%20makes%20the%20launch%20location%20agnostic%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20could%20be%20configured%20to%20fly%20with%204%2F5%2F6%2F7%20%5Bengines%5D%20which%20makes%20the%20launch%20cost%20the%20same%20across%20the%20spectrum%20of%20mass%20-%2030%20kg%20-%20300%20kg%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20has%20already%20attracted%20an%20investment%20of%2040%20million%20dollars%20and%20has%20a%20team%20of%20250%20members.%20%26quot%3BThe%20average%20age%20of%20employees%20at%20Agnikul%20is%2023%20years%20and%20all%20are%20fired%20up%20to%20innovate%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Moin%2C%20underscoring%20that%20India%20can%20become%20a%20hub%20for%20small%20satellite%20launches%20as%20more%20and%20more%20global%20companies%20are%20opting%20for%20constellations%20of%20satellites%20placed%20in%20low%20earth%20orbits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716871020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fd20ui6go_agnibaan-_625x300_28_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fchennai-start-ups-rocket-launch-game-changer-for-space-tech-called-off-5761350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Agnikul%20Cosmos%2C%20a%20pioneering%20private%20space%20start-up%20in%20India%2C%20faced%20yet%20another%20hurdle%20today%20as%20the%20test%20launch%20of%20their%20rocket%2C%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20(Suborbital%20Tech%20Demonstrator)%2C%20was%20called%20off%20just%20seconds%20before%20lift-off.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUr