C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStrong%20gales%20and%20heavy%20rain%20triggered%20by%20the%20first%20major%20cyclone%20of%20the%20year%20lashed%20the%20coastlines%20of%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20on%20Monday%2C%20killing%20at%20least%2016%20people%20and%20cutting%20power%20to%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20winds%20had%20not%20stopped%20as%20night%20fell%2C%20with%20water%20rising%20in%20many%20places%20and%20overwhelming%20drainage%20systems%2C%20Bangladeshi%20climate%20expert%20Liakath%20Ali%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20are%20stranded%20-%20it%20will%20be%20another%20long%20night%20ahead%20with%20millions%20not%20having%20electricity%20or%20shelter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20people%20having%20no%20idea%20of%20how%20damaged%20their%20homes%2C%20land%20and%20livestock%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECyclone%20Remal%20is%20the%20first%20of%20the%20frequent%20storms%20expected%20to%20pound%20the%20low-lying%20coasts%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20neighbours%20this%20year%20as%20climate%20change%20drives%20up%20surface%20temperatures%20at%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacking%20speeds%20of%20up%20to%20135%20kph%2C%20it%20crossed%20the%20area%20around%20Bangladesh's%20southern%20port%20of%20Mongla%20and%20the%20adjoining%20Sagar%20Islands%20in%20West%20Bengal%20late%20on%20Sunday%2C%20weather%20officials%20said%2C%20making%20landfall%20at%20about%209%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%208.4%20million%20people%2C%20including%203.2%20million%20children%2C%20are%20at%20high%20health%2C%20nutrition%2C%20sanitation%20and%20safety%20risk%2C%20said%20Sheldon%20Yett%2C%20UNICEF%20Representative%20to%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20disaster%20management%20chief%20Mijanur%20Rahman%20told%20Reuters%2C%20adding%20some%20victims%20died%20en%20route%20to%20shelters%20or%20when%20their%20homes%20or%20walls%20collapsed%2C%20or%20drowned%20during%20the%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20usually%20very%20reluctant%20to%20leave%20their%20livestock%20and%20homes%20to%20go%20to%20cyclone%20shelters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20wait%20until%20the%20last%20minute%20when%20it%20is%20often%20too%20late.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Minister%20for%20Disaster%20Management%20and%20Relief%20Mohibbur%20Rahman%20said%20the%20cyclone%20destroyed%20nearly%2035%2C000%20homes%20across%2019%20districts.%20An%20additional%20115%2C000%20homes%20were%20partially%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20areas%20remain%20waterlogged%2C%20and%20fish%20enclosures%20and%20trees%20have%20been%20devastated.%20As%20more%20information%20becomes%20available%2C%20the%20full%20scope%20of%20the%20impact%20will%20be%20clearer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMangrove%20Forests%20Flooded%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20four%20people%20were%20electrocuted%2C%20authorities%20said%2C%20taking%20the%20death%20toll%20in%20the%20state%20to%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20shut%20down%20electricity%20supply%20to%20some%20areas%20in%20advance%20to%20avoid%20accidents%2C%20while%20in%20many%20coastal%20towns%20fallen%20trees%20and%20snapped%20electricity%20lines%20further%20disrupted%20supply%2C%20power%20ministry%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%203%20million%20people%20in%20Bangladesh%20were%20without%20electricity%2C%20officials%20added.%20West%20Bengal%20authorities%20said%20at%20least%201%2C200%20power%20poles%20were%20uprooted%2C%20while%20300%20mud%20huts%20had%20been%20razed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladeshi%20State%20Minister%20for%20Power%20and%20Energy%20Nasrul%20Hamid%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20that%20Remal%20has%20caused%20extensive%20damage%20nationwide%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20be%20patient%20as%20repairs%20were%20under%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20crews%20began%20repairing%20the%20lines%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20wi