hild%20%26quot%3Bknocked%20the%20table%20with%20his%20foot%20and%20caused%20it%20to%20teeter%2C%20to%20almost%20topple%2C%20before%20it%20rights%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmediately%20%E2%80%93%20like%20a%20reflex%20%E2%80%93%20Malcolm%20hits%20him%20in%20the%20face%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Guardian's%20Jenny%20Kleeman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20heavy%20blow%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20slap%20with%20the%20palm%20of%20his%20hand%20direct%20to%20his%20two-year-old%20son's%20face%20that's%20firm%20enough%20for%20me%20to%20hear%20on%20my%20voice%20recorder%20when%20I%20play%20it%20back%20later.%20And%20Malcolm%20has%20done%20it%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20public%20place%2C%20in%20front%20of%20a%20journalist%2C%20who%20he%20knows%20is%20recording%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalcolm%20Collins%20resumed%20his%20conversation%20with%20the%20stunned%20reporter%20after%20telling%20his%20child%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%20but%20you%20gotta%20be%20nice%20in%20restaurants.%20No%2C%20Toastie.%20You're%20going%20to%20get%20bopped%20if%20you%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20afterward%2C%20the%20episode%20went%20viral%20on%20X%20%E2%80%94%20the%20platform%20owned%20by%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20whom%20Malcolm%20Collins%20was%20incidentally%20gushing%20over%20moments%20before%20striking%20his%20toddler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pro-natalist%20couple%20hits%20their%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FGrahamStarr%2Fstatus%2F1794376833364091036%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%20user%20said%2C%20sharing%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJesus%20Christ%20the%20kid%20is%20two!!!!%20My%20kid%20is%20two!!!!%20The%20idea%20of%20hitting%20her%20has%20simply%20never%20occurred%20to%20me%20and%20if%20you%20know%20any%20two-year-olds%20it%20should%20be%20obvious%20how%20obviously%20nuts%20it%20is%20to%20do%20this!!!!%26quot%3B%20another%20shared%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdennismhogan%2Fstatus%2F1794426573334200791%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Simone%20Collins%20said%20the%20toddler%2C%20named%20Torsten%20Savage%2C%20was%20intentionally%20acting%20out%2C%20and%20tipping%20over%20a%20table%20with%20glassware%20on%20top%20of%20it%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20deadly%20in%20a%20house%20with%20infants%26quot%3B%20if%20it%20were%20to%20happen%20at%20the%20couple's%20Pennsylvania%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20an%20incredibly%20sweet%2C%20smart%2C%20analytic%20kid%2C%20but%20he%20also%20has%20a%20major%20rebellious%20streak%20and%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20his%20twos.%20This%20is%20all%20to%20say%20that%20yes%2C%20100%25%2C%20Torsten%20was%20pushing%20boundaries%20and%20not%20acting%20unintentionally%2C%26quot%3B%20Simone%20Collins%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIncidents%20in%20which%20we%20'bop'%20our%20kids%20are%20unusual%E2%80%94usually%20when%20physical%20safety%20is%20at%20stake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20phone%2C%20Malcolm%20Collins%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bbopped%26quot%3B%20his%20son%20on%20the%20nose%20to%20jar%20him%2C%20not%20to%20hurt%20him.%20The%20couple%20chose%20the%20punishment%20specifically%20after%20observing%20%26quot%3Banimal%20parenting%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20across%20the%20nose%20is%20what%20we%20aim%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Malcolm%20Collins%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20I%20think%20it's%20better%20than%20a%20slap%20on%20the%20wrist%20is%20because%20it%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20painful%20to%20have%20the%20same%20impact.%20By%20that%2C%20what%20I%20mean%20is%20when%20somebody%20enters%20the%20space%20around%20your%20face%2C%20it%20is%20very%20shocking%20and%20very%20reorienting%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20in%20an%20emotional%20loop%2C%20which%20is%20easy%20for%20kids%20to%20get%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20you%20could%20achieve%20the%20same%20effect%20by%20hitting%20a%20child's%20wrist%20is%20to%20hit%20it%20large%20enough%20to%20cause%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20pain%2C%20which%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20do%2C%20but%20I%20can%20understand%20why%20visually%20people%20might%20be%2C%20'Oh%2C%20the%20slight%20hit%20on%20the%20nose%20or%20the%20face%20is%20really%20bad'%20because%20it%20looks%20visually%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20both%20said%20they%20found%20the%20backlash%20they%20faced%20on%20social%20media%20to%20be%20racist%20since%2C%20they%20argued%2C%20minorities%20often%20hit%20their%20children%20without%20the%20same%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20kind%20of%20shocked%20by%20the%20racism%20threaded%20throughout%20this%20recent%20controversy.%20It%20is%20pretty%20well-documented%20that%20African%20Americans%20and%20other%20minority%20groups%20practice%20corporal%20punishment%20much%20more%20than%20other%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20Simone%20Collins%20said%20via%20email%2C%20linking%20to%20a%20CNN%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2011%2F11%2F10%2Fus%2Fresearchers-african-americans-most-likely-to-use-physical-punishment%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalcolm%20Collins%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Buniquely%20offensive%26quot%3B%20to%20him%20considering%20%26quot%3Bthe%20majority%20of%20Americans%20practice%20some%20form%20of%20corporal%20punishment%2C%20as%20you%20can%20see%20from%20the%20statistics%20with%20specifically%20that%20being%20the%20minority%20groups%20of%20Americans.%20So%20yeah%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20an%20arguably%20racist%20position.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpronatalist-parents-dad-slapped-toddler-face-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2F