EThe%20slew%20of%20awards%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Social%20Impact%20India%20Award%20(2017)%20by%20the%20British%20Council%20and%20Entrepreneur%20Excellence%20Award%20by%20I.I.T.%20Delhi%20(2017)%2C%20Earthday%20Network%20Star%20(2020)%20among%20others%20%E2%80%94%20that%20colour%20her%20journey%20is%20great%2C%20she%20admits.%20But%20they%20cannot%20be%20compensation%20for%20the%20drudgery%20that%20women%20farmers%20go%20through%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20%E2%80%9CHelp%20them%20instead%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Guna%20Organics%20steps%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpadhyaya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20introduced%20certified%20organic%20and%20organic%20solar-dried%20products%20into%20the%20mainstream%20market%2C%20enhanced%20livelihoods%20by%2033%20percent%20and%20reversed%20migration%20from%2027%20to%2075%20households.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20conducted%20the%20Beat%20Plastic%20Pollution%20campaign%2C%20provided%20green%20training%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297056%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-trains-women-in-organic-farming-online-facebook-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskill-based%20training%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20corporates%2C%20schools%2C%20factories%2C%20farmer%20producer%20groups%2C%20and%20exporters%20helping%20them%20achieve%20sustainable%20development%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-4-1716442844.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20oximeter%20distribution%20was%20done%20by%20Neha%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20to%20ensure%20access%20to%20healthcare%20in%20remote%20Ladakh%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-med