0prevent%20farmers%20from%20lugging%20around%2010%20litre%20spray%20pumps%20on%20their%20shoulders%2C%20which%20you%20have%20to%20refill%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20his%20sketch%2C%20some%20old%20cycles%20and%20went%20to%20a%20welder%20who%20helped%20him%20make%20the%20machine.%20His%20first%20prototype%20was%20a%20machine%20which%20could%20sow%20seeds%20and%20spray%20pesticides.%20Ramdhan%20laughs%20as%20he%20shares%20that%20his%20machine%20is%20a%20product%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%3C%2Fem%3E%20(hack).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesting%20the%20machine%20was%20easy%20as%20his%20father%20became%20the%20guinea%20pig.%20Seeing%20the%20practicality%20of%20it%2C%20farmers%20from%20nearby%20also%20borrowed%20it%2C%20validating%20the%20teenager%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313817%2Fmangaluru-farmer-innovation-tree-scooter-helps-farmers-cut-cost-harvest-areca-palms-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarmers%20liked%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20though%20they%20had%20to%20manually%20push%20it%2C%20it%20was%20better%20than%20renting%20machines.%20I%20wanted%20to%20improve%20it%20further%20as%20I%20saw%20that%20it%20was%20helping%20them%20practically%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequent%20prize%20money%20won%20at%20national%20science%20fairs%20helped%20Ramdhan%20add%20a%20motor%2C%20batteries%20and%20solar%20panel%2C%20making%20it%20electric.%20Started%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%2010%2C%20he%20had%20made%20his%20final%20and%20third%20prototype%20by%20the%20time%20he%20was%20in%20Class%2012.%20The%20entire%20machine%20was%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20machine%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20is%20in%20essence%2C%20a%20modified%20cycle%2C%20with%20a%20battery%2C%20solar%20panel%2C%20spray%20pumps%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20a%20weed%20remover%20in%20the%20front.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F1lhwATLxZKM%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%20invents%20a%20Solar%20powered%20Weed%20Killing%20Machine%20%23svc%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multi-tasking%20machine%20can%20perform%20four%20critical%20farming%20operations%20%E2%80%93%20cleaning%20weeds%2C%20drilling%20seeds%2C%20spraying%20fertiliser%20and%20laying%20manure.%20It%20works%20on%20both%20solar%20power%20and%20has%20a%20battery%2C%20for%20cloudy%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20customised%20for%20length%20and%20folded%20for%20easy%20transportation.%20The%20design%20incorporates%20easily%20adjustable%20parts%20and%20attachments%20that%20mimic%20the%20functionality%20of%20larger%2C%20more%20expensive%20farming%20machinery%2C%20making%20it%20an%20ideal%20solution%20for%20small-scale%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20can%20do%20all%20these%20different%20tasks%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20saving%20time%20and%20energy.%20You%20can%20remove%20weeds%20and%20spray%20fertilisers%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20It%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20picking%20up%20heavy%20spray%20tanks%20and%20hiring%20labourers%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ramdhan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20bulb%20for%20farmers%20who%20wish%20to%20work%20at%20night%20and%20has%20a%20charger%20for%20the%20battery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamdhan%E2%80%99s%20father%20beams%20with%20pride%20as%20he%20speaks%20about%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noref