20fertiliser.%20How%20much%20direct%20sunlight%20should%20be%20given%20was%20also%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20she%20learnt%20that%20it%20was%20ideal%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20early%20morning%2C%20between%207%20to%208%20am%2C%20the%20best%20time%20to%20do%20pest%20control%20was%20either%20before%206%20am%20or%20after%206%20pm%2C%20and%20fruit%20trees%20generally%20need%20more%20water.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20the%20needs%20of%20each%20vegetable%2C%20flower%20and%20fruit%20was%20different%2C%20and%20she%20would%20have%20to%20work%20her%20way%20around%20that%20through%20trial%20and%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGardening%20as%20therapy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20initial%20hiccups%2C%20her%20plants%20started%20growing%20beautifully.%20Seeing%20her%20vegetables%20thrive%20gave%20her%20the%20confidence%20to%20start%20growing%20fruits.%20She%20also%20had%20a%20more%20important%20motive%20%E2%80%93%20encouraging%20her%20son%20to%20eat%20fruits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6Q2xS5vaPL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6Q2xS5vaPL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%