%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FDhiren-Solanki-1716215826-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FDhiren-Solanki-1716215826-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350585%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFollowing%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20advice%2C%20Dhiren%20quit%20his%20fantasy%20of%20landing%20a%20government%20job%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDonkey%20milk%20%E2%80%93%20a%20hidden%20gem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20his%20father%2C%20Dhiren%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20aspiration%20was%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20teaching.%20So%2C%20after%20completing%20his%20schooling%20in%20science%2C%20he%20started%20preparing%20for%20the%20government%20examinations%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20limited%20vacancies%20for%20government%20jobs%20and%20there%20is%20too%20much%20competition%20in%20this%20field.%20Anyway%2C%20I%20appeared%20for%20many%20state%20and%20central-level%20examinations%20in%20February%202020%20but%20I%20did%20not%20get%20any%20results.%20I%20was%20sitting%20idle%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%20and%20was%20just%20waiting%20for%20my%20results.%20I%20was%20getting%20demotivated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202021%2C%20his%20father%20read%20about%20the%20donkey-rearing%20business%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20concept%20was%20not%20at%20all%20popularised%20in%20the%20North.%20Although%20there%20is%20little%20demand%20for%20donkey%20milk%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%20has%20huge%20demand%20in%20countries%20like%20Turkey%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20China%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20people%20are%20bothered%20by%20soaring%20prices%20of%20cow%20and%2